# Stripe — test mode for local dev. Get keys from Stripe Dashboard →
# Developers → API keys (test mode toggle ON in top-right).
# Webhook secret comes from `stripe listen --forward-to localhost:8788/api/payments/webhook`
# (Stripe CLI) — prints a whsec_* on first run.
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Sentry: DSNs are hardcoded in src/lib/sentry.ts and functions/_lib/sentry.ts
# (DSNs are public-by-design; committing them is the documented pattern).
# No env vars needed here for Sentry — rotation is a code change + push.
